# Code owners for Goobers.
# Owners are requested for review automatically and, once branch protection (#3)
# requires CODEOWNER review, must approve before merge.
# Order matters: the last matching pattern wins.
#
# NOTE: as the project grows, replace @masra91 with an org team
# (e.g. @Agent-Clubhouse/maintainers) so ownership isn't tied to one account.

# Default owner for everything in the repo.
*                       @masra91

# Build/CI tooling — the enforced merge gate.
/.github/               @masra91
/Makefile               @masra91
/.golangci.yml          @masra91

# Tutor config-only write-boundary (#104 / T4). selfhost/ is the dogfood
# instance's config root — the only tree the Tutor is path-scoped to write.
# Because Tutor PRs land in the same repo as platform code here, CODEOWNER
# review on this root is the required human gate before a self-tuning config
# change merges (structural credential enforcement rides #35).
# See docs/guides/tutor-write-boundary.md.
/selfhost/              @masra91
